title: Not worth the price. Doesn't seem like an Adidas product
body: One star because there isn't an option to rate below that. Two set of stripes and Adidas written in the sole is not something you find in authentic Adidas products. The elastic didn't even last for 2 - 3 washes. Would not recommend this product. The products you find on streets were hawkers sell 3 pairs for Rs 100 is better than this.
